  m_text: "The first method is (that you have to develop) the stakeholder analysis.
    All the groups/people (organizations, institutions) interested in the project
    are stakeholders.\n\nYou will get more information about the product. Stakeholders
    are viewed according to resource investment. e.g. if 2 resources invested then
    we can see \u201CCustomer\u201D, if 3 then \u201CTUV\u201D. According to the
    quality, stakeholders are mapped/appear into the quadrants.\r"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
