  m_text: 'The function hierarchy describes the overall functional behavior of the
    system, regardless of the realization. The foundation for the functional hierarchy
    are the usecases. Functions are derived from the list of requirements and describe
    the functions as solution neutral. It serves to structure the overall function
    of a system until suitable solution elements can be found for the sub-functions.  '
