      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "The users can now invest in the different methods. \n\nDiscuss amongst
    all the colleagues and make a collective decision.\n\nIf the players want to
    refresh the concepts of the different methods they can just \nclick on the buttons
    with the respective method names and they would be able to \nsee the method descriptions,
    which might help them make better investment \ndecisions.\n\nThe users can use
    the scrollbar to see all the methods available to them for investment.\n"
