  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "For each role different method or aspect of the project might be important,
    and they should invest more of their resources in that method. Each player should
    invest at least a minimum number of resources in each method. All the methods
    have a certain minimum threshold value for each player, failing to meet which
    will result in an insufficient quality of a method for the entire team. Once
    the team is satisfied with their investments, they can proceed to Method Development.
    \r\n\r\n\r\nHint: If players are not satisfied with the investments made in one
    round, the players can choose to spend another round in the same phase and spend
    more resources and better develop the methods.\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
