  m_text: "Finally, the application scenarios provides a situation-specific view
    of the system. The initial situation are given and the expected functionalities
    are defined in the form of requirements and these functionalities (requirements)
    needed to be developed further as application of the product (grill). \n\nApplication
    scenarios are often specified in interaction with the system environment. The
    application scenarios offer a view of the system behavior."
