  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Now its time to invest in Phase 4.\r\n\r\nSimilar to previous phase, these
    methods should be unlocked by the players. By using resources, the individual
    artefacts of the methods are unlocked and the methods are gradually developed. 
    \r\n\r\nIn the successive screen, players should invest resources in each of
    the methods which will have direct influence on the quality of the product. Hence
    the players should invest wisely in each methods based on the number of resources
    alloted.\r\n\r\nImportant Information: While you are investing in the Phase 4,
    you also have an advantage of investing resources in the methods of previous
    phases. By doing so, you can increase the overall quality of the product."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
